of the National Science Foundation operated under cooperative agreement
by Associated Universities, Inc. Appendix A and Figs. {[}see full text]-
{[}see full text] are only available in electronic form at
http://www.aanda.org},
  timestamp = {2015-08-03 15:41:20},
  urldate = {2015-07-08},
  journal = {Astronomy and Astrophysics},
  author = {Isella, A. and Testi, L. and Natta, A. and Neri, R. and Wilner, D. and Qi, C.},
  month = jul,
